  "texts": [
    "Lastly, this study utilized GPT-2, an earlier version of what is now known as ChatGPT or GPT-4, but that was the current technology at the time of this study.",
    "Advancements with this technology have resulted in significant observed improvements, such as successfully passing standardized exams and submitting graduate-level written compositions (van Boom, 2023).",
    "Hence, it is fair to assume that ongoing developments in GenAI will continue to result in improved text compositions compared to those tested against human compositions.",
    "Works of Weber-Wulff et al.",
    "2023 and Elkhatat et al."
  ]
}